                    <event>
                        <desc>
                            With regard to the mutilation of <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/2772">Thomas</persName>,<persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/51">Severus</persName>advises<persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/2614">Aurelius</persName>to allow<persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/2772">him</persName>his priestly office if the mutilation was performed by a physician because of an illness, but to deny him if<persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/2772">he</persName>mutilated himself.
                        </desc>
                        <ptr target="http://syriaca.org/keyword/authority http://syriaca.org/keyword/body http://syriaca.org/keyword/shame http://syriaca.org/keyword/illness http://syriaca.org/keyword/physicians http://syriaca.org/keyword/priests http://syriaca.org/keyword/suffering"/>
